title: Fighting For My Man
itunes:title: Fighting For My Man
description:
Dear Steve and Shirley my husband and I have known each other since we were seven and 11 years old. Throughout the years we've had often on relationships it didn't matter if we were exclusive or not we always found a way to be together. We finally got married. We have been separated for four years until we found our way back to one another.
